@Reverse_Hate wrote:

You missed a brace. ({ or })

Change the code I gave you to:

Code (Java): [Select]
if ((username.equalsIgnoreCase(“name”)) || (username.equalsIgnoreCase(“name2”))) {
rights = 3;
}
}

(I’m assuming this block is at the end of a method because what you posted only contained one opening brace and two closing)

Tell me the results when you’re done.


That worked, but in a different source I’m trying to get working I have the 37 errors, if I can’t fix I’ll just use the source that you helped me with but I’d really appreciate it if you could give me a little help on the 37 errors. But, the owner part worked.
